260
00:20:01,168 --> 00:20:14,773
No, no. I gotta go home sometime.

261
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
You gonna be okay?

262
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Yeah.

263
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Hey, Mom. Look what I just found on the floor.

264
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
What? That's Paul's watch.

265
00:20:14,773 --> 00:20:34,833
You just put it back where you found it.

266
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Oh, boy.

267
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
All right. Good night, everybody.

268
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Good night.

269
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Oh, I'm…

270
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Oh, sorry.

271
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Oh, no, no, go, go, go.

272
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
No, I don't want it.

273
00:20:34,833 --> 00:20:42,456
Split it?

274
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Okay.

275
00:20:42,456 --> 00:20:50,187
Okay. You know, you probably didn't know this, but back in high school, I had a, um… major crush on you.

276
00:20:50,187 --> 00:20:52,199
