277
00:20:52,199 --> 00:20:55,480
You did?

278
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Oh, okay.

279
00:20:55,480 --> 00:20:58,691
I always figured you just thought I was Monica's geeky older brother.

280
00:20:58,691 --> 00:20:59,785
I did.

281
00:20:59,785 --> 00:21:04,715
Oh.

282
00:21:04,715 --> 00:21:07,442
Listen, do you think…

283
00:21:07,442 --> 00:21:13,258
and try not to let my intense vulnerability become any kind of a factor here…

284
00:21:13,258 --> 00:21:18,528
but do you think it would be okay if I asked you out sometime, maybe?

285
00:21:18,528 --> 00:21:23,124
Yeah, maybe.

286
00:21:23,124 --> 00:21:25,624
Okay. Okay, maybe I will.

287
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Good night.

288
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,000
Good night.

